lead_paragraph: Chase Kalisz qualified fastest in the 400-meter individual medley preliminaries Sunday at the U.S. Olympic swimming trials with Ryan Lochte trying to shake off the cobwebs on the meet's first day.

headline.main: Lochte Finishes 2nd in 400 IM Heats at US Olympic Trials
